annotations.title: The 5 Easiest TEQUILA Cocktails

textContent:
2oz (60ml) tequila
.5oz (15ml) pineapple juice
.5oz (15ml) lime juice
.5oz (15ml) simple syrup
5 thai basil leaves

Muddle 4 Thai basil leaves into pineapple juice
Add rest of liquid ingredients and shake with ice for 15 seconds
Double strain into a chilled coupe glass
Garnish with another Thai basil leaf
